6061 - Credit Unions, Federally Chartered Summary > COASTLINE CREDIT UNION LIMITED (formerly MACLEAY MUTUAL CREDIT UNION LIMITED.) is an Australian public company. Its operations cover credit unions, not federally chartered. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. COASTLINE CREDIT UNION LIMITED is headquartered in West Kempsey, New South Wales. It is headed by chairman & director Vanessa Gene Mcneilly. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $36.99 million. Its net profit totalled $6.67 million. COASTLINE CREDIT UNION LIMITED forms part of the finance, insurance, and real estate industry sector.
